        <dc:title>Comparison of Stepped Care Delivery Against a Single, Empirically Validated Cognitive-Behavioral Therapy Program for Youth With Anxiety: A Randomized Clinical Trial.</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>This randomized clinical trial compared stepped care with a single empirically validated CBT program in 281 anxious youth. The two approaches did not differ significantly on outcomes, while stepped care used less therapist time.</dcterms:abstract>
        <dc:date>2017</dc:date>
