        <dc:title>Stepped Care Versus Stratified Care for Youth with Anxiety Disorders: a Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial.</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>In this pilot randomized trial, stepped care was compared with stratified care for youth anxiety disorders. The study found the trial was feasible, but it was explicitly not powered to compare efficacy.</dcterms:abstract>
