        <dc:title>Youth Anxiety: The Moderating Effects of Accommodation and Emotional Warmth</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>This moderation study found that family accommodation changed the relationship between emotional warmth and youth anxiety. It is relevant as an interaction paper, but the moderator and predictor were family variables rather than digital exposure.</dcterms:abstract>
