        <dc:title>A Systematic Review of Family Accommodation in Autistic Youth: Anxiety Disorders, Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder, and Restricted and Repetitive Behaviors</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>Using PRISMA guidelines, this review summarizes family accommodation in caregivers of autistic youth in relation to comorbid anxiety, OCD, and restricted/repetitive behaviors, and how accommodation is addressed in treatment.</dcterms:abstract>
