        <dcterms:abstract>This preregistered meta-analysis identified 26 trials (k=157, N=4098) and found parent-focused interventions had a significant medium effect on children's anxiety (d=-0.59; 95% CI [-0.92, -0.26]).</dcterms:abstract>
